# Notes Page Revolution: 3 Layout Architectures

## Status: COMPLETE

## Overview
Complete rebuild of the Notes page providing 3 distinct, user-selectable layout architectures to address user feedback about cramped sidebar, limited editor space, and lack of customization.

## Requirements
- [x] Three-Column Layout (Apple Notes/Bear style)
- [x] File Tree Layout (Obsidian/VS Code style)
- [x] Tabbed Sidebar Layout (Notion style)
- [x] Layout switching mechanism (modal + keyboard shortcut)
- [x] Persisted layout preference
- [x] Extracted components from monolithic Notes.tsx
- [x] Keyboard navigation for folder tree and notes list
- [x] Reduced motion support

